menu "CH422G-controlled SDSPI"

config SDSPI_DIAG_EXIO_SCAN
    bool "Enable EXIO scan diagnostic for SD CS"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, a diagnostic routine can temporarily probe EXIO0..EXIO7
        as potential SD chip-select lines to detect miswired CS routing. This
        is intended for bring-up only; keep disabled in production builds.

endmenu

